title: Letter To The Exiles Discography 2008-2013 (4 Releases)
description:
--------------------------------------------------------------
LETTER TO THE EXILES DISCOGRAPHY
--------------------------------------------------------------

This discography may or may not be complete.  It contains the following 4 releases...

 * 2008 - A Call To Arms EP
 * 2010 - The Shadow Line
 * 2012 - Make Amends
 * 2013 - Still Moving Still Breathing EP

Letter To The Exiles is a metalcore band from Long Island, New York. The band formed in 2008 and are currently signed to Facedown Records.

Glory Above,
TorrentTracts - October 2013
